132nd MAINE LEGISLATURE
FIRST SPECIAL SESSION-2025
Legislative Document No. 1235
H.P. 810 House of Representatives, March 25, 2025
An Act to Establish Transparency in Opioid Settlement Funds
Allocated to Municipalities or Counties
Reference to the Committee on Judiciary suggested and ordered printed.
ROBERT B. HUNT
Clerk
Presented by Representative ROEDER of Bangor.
Cosponsored by Senator BALDACCI of Penobscot and
Representatives: CLOUTIER of Lewiston, DRINKWATER of Milford, FAIRCLOTH of
